eraldic gurges (whirlpool) Gorges.svg|25px]]Gorges of [[Warleigh, Bickleigh]]  :  ''Argent, three gorgets azure one within the other '' (''Argent, a gurges azure'')\n*[[File:GorgesArms(Modern).png|25px]]Gorges (modern)   :  ''Lozengy or and azure, a chevron gules  ''\n*[[File:GlanvilleArms.png|25px]]Glanvill of Tavistock  :  ''Azure, three saltires or ''\n*[[File:GrenvilleArms.svg|25px]]Grenville of Bideford  :  ''Gules, three clarions or  ''\n*Grass of Teign Grass  :  ''Ermine, a fess between three cinquefoils gules ''\n*[[File:Arms of Grey Family.svg|25px]]Grey, Marquess of Dorset  :  ''Barry of six argent and azure, in chief three torteaux a label ermine ''\n*Gray of Exeter  :  ''Or, on a bend azure three martlets argent ''\n*Gatpath of Gatpath  :  ''Argent, a chevron between three goat\u2019s heads erased gules ''\n*Grane of Monk Okehampton  :  ''On a bend cotised three mascles '' (tinctures unknown)\n*Grenham of Woborneford  :  ''Vert, a chief or ''\n*Gervais of Exeter:<ref>[[Walter Gervais]], Mayor of Exeter and founder of the Exe Bridge, [[John Prince (biographer)|Prince, John]], (1643\u20131723) The Worthies of Devon, 1810 edition, London[https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=HHNEAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA408&lpg=PA408&dq=william+gervais+mayor+of+exeter&source=bl&ots=My1Jp6GzcO&sig=ACfU3U3o995QXB1Xi9GdB3dhrKKFiBfR_g&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjOw-fTp_roAhX1QEEAHR5iBRoQ6AEwAnoECAcQAQ#v=onepage&q=william%20gervais%20mayor%20of%20exeter&f=true]</ref> ''Quarterly argent and gules, a bordure vert bezant\u00e9e ''\n*[[File:JarvysArms.png|25px]]Gervays/Jarvys of Exeter:<ref>[[Walter Gervais]], Mayor of Exeter and founder of the Exe Bridge, [[John Prince (biographer)|Prince, John]], (1643\u20131723) The Worthies of Devon, 1810 edition, London</ref>  ''Argent, six feathers sable 3,2,1 ''\n\n===H===\n*Haccombe of [[Haccombe]] :  ''Argent, three bends sable''\n*Hach of [[Woolleigh, Beaford]] & of [[Aller, South Molton]]:  ''Gules, two demi-lions guardant or''\n*Halse of Kenedon :  ''Sabl