ms.png|70px]]\n|''Azure, an estoile of six points issuing from a crescent argent''\n|[[Exeter]]\n|-\n|Molford\n|[[File:MolfordArms.png|70px]]\n|''Sable, a fess ermine between three swans argent''\n|[[South Molton]]\n|-\n|[[William de Moyon|Mohun]]\n|[[File:MohunArms.png|70px]]\n|''Or, a cross engrailed sable''\n|[[Tavistock]]; [[Mohuns Ottery]], [[Luppitt]]; [[Tor Mohun]] ([[Dunster Castle]], Somerset; [[Hall, Lanteglos-by-Fowey]], Cornwall; [[Boconnoc]], Cornwall)\n|-\n|[[George Monck, 1st Duke of Albemarle|Monck]]\n|[[File:Monck arms.svg|70px]]\n|''Gules, a chevron between three lion's heads erased argent''\n|[[Potheridge]], [[Merton, Devon|Merton]]\n|-\n|Moore\n|[[File:MooreOfMooreArms.PNG|70px]]\n|''Argent, a chevron between three [[Black grouse|moorcocks]] sable crested gules''<ref>Pole, p.493, field ''argent''; Vivian, p.574 ''azure''</ref>\n|Moore, \"near Tavistock\";<ref>Pole, p.220</ref> [[Broadwoodwidger]]; [[Upcott, Cheriton Fitzpaine]]\n|-\n|[[John Moore (bishop of Ely)|Moore]]\n|[[File:Moore OfMooreHayes Devon Arms.png|70px]]\n|''Ermine, on a chevron azure three cinquefoils or''\n|[[Moor Hayes]], [[Cullompton]]\n|-\n|More\n|[[File:More OfBroadclyst Arms.png|70px]]\n|''Sable, three garbs argent a bordure gobony or and gules''\n|[[Broadclyst]]\n|-\n|Moulton\n|[[File:MoultonArms.png|70px]]\n|''Per pale argent and ermine three bars gules''\n|[[Cullompton]]\n|\n|}\n\n===N===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Name !! Escutcheon !! Blazon !! Seat, parish\n|-\n|[[Robert Lydston Newcombe|Newcombe]]\n|[[File:NewcombeArms.png|70px]]\n|''Argent, a fess embattled between two escallops in pale sable''\n|Great Worthy, [[Drewsteignton]]; Easton, South Teign, [[Drewsteignton]]?;<ref>''The Newcombe family of Chagford & Exeter'', Peter R. Newcombe, 2005-17 [http://www.newcombe.info/Newcombe%20of%20Chagford.html]</ref> Exeter, St David's; [[Starcross]], [[Kenton, Devon|Kenton]]\n|-\n|Newcourt\n|[[File:NewcourtArms.png|70px]]\n|''Sable, a bend ermine between two eagles with tw